OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight low cloud mostly
OL,6,Fburning off this morning but may
OL,7,Flinger into the afternoon across
OL,8,FAngus. Otherwise dry with some spells
OL,9,Fof sunshine. Warm inland, east coast
OL,10,Fcooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will be mainly dry with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud. A few showers across
OL,16,FWestern Tayside later.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FMainly cloudy with some
OL,19,Fshowery rain, but drier with some
OL,20,Fbrightness across towards the east
OL,21,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
